Name: vctube
Version: 1.2
Summary: A pakage for crawling and processing audio, caption from Youtube
Home-page: https://github.com/zldzmfoq12/aud-crawler
Author: Seugnhun Jeong
Author-email: zldzmfoq12@naver.com
